OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Sally Simmonds
OL,7,Freports on Trevor MacGuire's
OL,8,Fincredible recovery
OL,10,FAn NHS worker who was left blind and
OL,11,Fbrain damaged after a random attack at
OL,12,Fa busy hospital has learned to ride a
OL,13,Ftandem bike after being inspired by an
OL,14,Finterview he saw on ITV News.
OL,16,FTrevor MacGuire was struck on the head
OL,17,Fthree times with a pick axe by one of
OL,18,Fhis colleagues while working as a
OL,19,Fproject manager at Central Middlesex
OL,20,FHospital in London hospital last June.
